<style>
  * {
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;

    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  body header {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  body header section {
    display: flex;
  }

  body header section aside {
    width: calc(50% - 4px);
  }

  body header section aside+aside {
    margin-left: 8px;
  }

  body header section#metadata {
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  body header section div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  body header section div+div {
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  body header section div strong {
    min-width: 70px;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  body header section div span {
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }

  body header section+section {
    border-top: 1px solid black;
    margin-top: 4px;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  body header div#table {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    border: 1px solid black;
  }

  body header div#table div#tableHeader,
  header div#table div#tableBody {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  body header div#table div#tableHeader {
    border-bottom: 1px solid black;
  }

  body header div#table div#tableHeader div {
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  body header div#table div#tableHeader div,
  body header div#table div#tableBody div {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2px 4px;
    width: 80px;
  }

  body header div#table div#tableHeader div+div,
  body header div#table div#tableBody div+div {
    border-left: 1px solid black;
  }

  div#content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  div#content div#tableHeader {
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 1px solid black;
  }

  div#content div#tableBody div#tableRow {
    border-bottom: 1px dotted black;
    border-left: 1px dotted black;
    border-right: 1px dotted black;
  }

  div#content div#tableHeader div {
    text-align: center;
  }

  div#content div#tableHeader div,
  div#content div#tableBody div#tableRow div {
    padding: 2px 4px;
  }

  div#content div#tableHeader div+div {
    border-left: 1px solid black;
  }

  div#content div#tableBody div#tableRow div+div {
    border-left: 1px dotted black;
  }

  div#content div#tableHeader,
  div#content div#tableBody div#tableRow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
  }

  div#content div#factoryCode {
    width: 45px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  div#content div#code {
    width: 40px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  div#content div#description {
    flex: 1;
    text-align: left !important;
  }

  div#content div#packing {
    width: 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  div#content div#unity {
    width: 25px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  div#content div#requestedCount {
    width: 60px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  div#content div#ipi {
    width: 30px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  div#content div#liquidValue {
    width: 50px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  div#content div#amountValue {
    width: 50px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  footer {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  footer div#totals {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;

    border: 1px solid black;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row+div#row {
    border-top: 1px solid black;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row div#tuple+div#tuple {
    border-left: 1px solid black;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row div#tuple {
    display: flex;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row div#tuple strong {
    border-right: 1px solid black;
    display: block;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row div#tuple span {
    display: block;
    width: 40px;
    text-align: right;
  }

  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row div#tuple strong,
  footer div#totals aside div#table div#row div#tuple span {
    padding: 2px 4px;
  }

  footer div#annotations {
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  footer div#annotations ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 4px 0 8px;
  }

  footer div#annotations ul li {
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  footer div#informations {
    line-height: 14px;
  }
</style>

<body>
  <header>
    <section id="metadata">
      <div>
        <strong>Nº do Pedido</strong>
        <span>{{ number }}</span>
      </div>

      <div>
        <strong>Emissão</strong>
        <span>{{ emittedAt }}</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="fromData">
      <aside>
        <div>
          <strong>Empresa</strong>
          <span>{{ buyerName }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Endereço</strong>
          <span>{{ buyerAddress }}, {{ buyerNumber }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Cidade, UF</strong>
          <span>{{ buyerCity }}, {{ buyerUF }}</span>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <aside>
        <div>
          <strong>CNPJ</strong>
          <span>{{ buyerCNPJ }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>IE</strong>
          <span>{{ buyerIE }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>CEP</strong>
          <span>{{ buyerCEP }}</span>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section id="toData">
      <aside>
        <div>
          <strong>Fornecedor</strong>
          <span>{{ providerName }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>CNPJ</strong>
          <span>{{ providerCNPJ }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Endereço</strong>
          <span>{{ providerAddress }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Cidade</strong>
          <span>{{ providerCity }}, {{ providerState }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Telefone</strong>
          <span>{{ providerPhone }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Condições de Pagamento</strong>
          <span>{{ deadline }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Frete</strong>
          <span>{{ freight }}</span>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <aside>
        <div>
          <strong>Código</strong>
          <span>{{ providerCode }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>Bairro</strong>
          <span>{{ providerNeighborhood }}</span>
        </div>

        <div>
          <strong>CEP</strong>
          <span>{{ providerCEP }}</span>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <div id="table">
      <div id="tableHeader">
        <div>Faturamento</div>
        <div>Embarque</div>
        <div>Entrega</div>
      </div>
      <div id="tableBody">
        <div>{{ billingAt }}</div>
        <div>{{ boardingAt }}</div>
        <div>{{ expectedDeliveryAt }}</div>
      </div>
      </table>
  </header>

  <div id="content">
    <div id="tableHeader">
      <div id="factoryCode">Cód Fáb.</div>
      <div id="code">Código</div>
      <div id="description">Descrição</div>
      <div id="packing">Embalagem</div>
      <div id="unity">Und</div>
      <div id="requestedCount">Qtd. Pedida</div>
      <div id="ipi">Vl. IPI</div>
      <div id="liquidValue">P. Líquido</div>
      <div id="amountValue">Vl. Total</div>
    </div>

    <div id="tableBody">
      {{{ body }}}
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div id="totals">
      <aside>
        <div id="table">
          <div id="row">
            <div id="tuple">
              <strong style="width: 45px;">Itens</strong>
              <span>{{ productCount }}</span>
            </div>

            <div id="tuple">
              <strong style="width: 60px;">Base ICMS</strong>
              <span>{{ amountICMSBase }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="row">
            <div id="tuple">
              <strong style="width: 45px;">Volumes</strong>
              <span>{{ amountVolume }}</span>
            </div>

            <div id="tuple">
              <strong style="width: 60px;">Valor ICMS</strong>
              <span>{{ amountICMSValue }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <aside>
        <div id="table">
          <div id="row">
            <div id="tuple">
              <strong style="width: 90px;">Total Líquido</strong>
              <span style="width: 50px;">{{ totalAmountValue }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <div id="annotations">
      <strong>Observações</strong>

      <ul>
        {{#if observationNumber1}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber1 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if observationNumber2}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber2 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if observationNumber3}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber3 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if observationNumber4}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber4 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if observationNumber5}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber5 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if observationNumber6}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber6 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
        {{#if observationNumber7}}
        <li>{{ observationNumber7 }}</li>
        {{/if}}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div id="informations">
      <strong>AGENDAMENTO DE CARGA</strong><br />
      Dias: de 2ª a 6ª feira<br />
      Horário: das 07:30h até 17:00h<br />
      Pausa p/ almoço: das 11:30h às 13:00h<br />
      O setor de Logística da DANTAS recebe somente cargas devidamente pré-agendadas e confirmadas.<br />
      • Contatos: <strong>KATIA VIRGÍNIO (83) 9.9135-0905</strong> e/ou <strong>ARTUR BISMARK (83)
        9.9362-9201</strong><br />
      • Agendamento via e-mail com arquivo anexo XML e PDF do DANFE para agendamento@dantasdistribuidora.com.br<br />
      • Arquivo DANFE (PDF) e arquivo XML da Nota Fiscal para recebimento@dantasdistribuidora.com.br<br />
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
